N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8131.20 - Town of DeWitt

State Regulations
(a) [Repealed]
(b) Kinne Street between

Route 298 and Molloy Road. (c) Molloy Road between Town Line Road and Northern Boulevard. (d) [Repealed]
(e) Vincent Drive between Town Line Road and

Smith Transfer terminal. (f) Boss

Road between Joy Drive and Red Star Express terminal. (g) Falso Drive between Molloy Road and

Roadway Express terminal. (h) Terminal Road between Schuyler Road and end of road. (i) Eastern Avenue between Commerce Boulevard
and ABF Freight Terminal. (j) Chrysler Drive between Route 298 and Fly Road; provided, however, that this
route shall be used only between the hours of 9 a.m. and 3 p.m., and from 6
p.m. to 6 a.m. Monday through Friday. Use of this route will be permitted all
day on Saturday and Sunday. (k) Route 290 (James Street) between Thompson Road and the Wegmans store at 4438

James Street. (l) Myers Road
between Fly Road and its dead end at the Northern Plastics Company trucking
terminal. (m) Fisher Road. Fisher

Road between Route 290 (Manlius Avenue) and the Cumberland Transportation truck
terminal, a distance of 0.3+- mile. Notes
